<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bug Tracking System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheet/style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <a href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo">
            </a>
        </div>
        <a href="/"><h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-blue-600">Bug Tracking System</h1></a>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/bugReport">Report a Bug</a>
            <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div id="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Welcome to <a href="/"><strong class="st">Bug Tracking System</strong></a>, the ultimate bug tracking and issue management platform designed to help teams streamline their development processes. Whether you’re working on small projects or large-scale systems, our tool ensures bugs are tracked, prioritized, and resolved efficiently.</p>
        
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to simplify bug reporting and resolution for development teams. We believe that well-organized issue management is key to delivering high-quality software and enhancing user experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="container">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Simple bug reporting:</strong> Easily submit bugs with detailed information.</li>
                <li><strong>Task prioritization:</strong> Assign priority levels to issues based on severity.</li>
                <li><strong>Seamless integrations:</strong> Connect with tools like GitHub, Slack, and more.</li>
                <li><strong>Real-time collaboration:</strong> Collaborate with your team in real-time with notifications and status updates.</li>
                <li><strong>Detailed analytics:</strong> Monitor progress and generate insightful reports to help you improve your development cycle.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div id="container">
            <h2>Who Can Use It</h2>
            <p>Our platform is designed for development teams of all sizes—from startups and open-source projects to large enterprise organizations. Whether you’re a developer, QA tester, or project manager, our intuitive interface will make your bug tracking process smoother and more efficient.</p>
        
        </div>
        <div id="container">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>User-friendly interface:</strong> Designed with simplicity and productivity in mind.</li>
                <li><strong>Customizable workflows:</strong> Tailor the platform to fit your team's unique workflow.</li>
                <li><strong>Excellent support:</strong> Get assistance from our dedicated customer support team whenever needed.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div id="container">
            <h2>Get Started</h2>
            <p>Ready to streamline your bug tracking process? <a class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700" href="/signup">Sign up today</a> and start tracking and resolving issues faster than ever before! Explore our demo or <a class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700" href="/contact">contact our team</a> for more information.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="information">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-blue-600">Assigned Bugs</h2>
        <table id="bugTable">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Bug ID</th>
                    <th>Title</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                    <th>Severity</th>
                    <th>Action</th>
                </tr>
            <tbody>
                <% if (bugs && bugs.length > 0) { %>
                    <% bugs.forEach(bugs => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= bugs.BugID %></td>
                            <td><%= bugs.Title %></td>
                            <td><%= bugs.Status %></td>
                            <td><%= bugs.Severity %></td>
                            <td><a href="/bugdetail/<%= bugs.BugID %>">View Details</a></td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }) %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p>No Bug to display.</p>
                <% } %>
            </tbody>
                
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <!-- Fetch and display bugs here dynamically from backend -->
            </tbody>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/javascript/index.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>